=== ASTEROID_IMPACT ===
# id: 43
# title: The Asteroid Impact
# chinese_title: 小行星撞击
# category: Hazard
# mode: dungeon

The station shudders as a rogue asteroid grazes the hull. Alarms wail and emergency lights paint everything in red. A breach opens in the outer wall, and atmosphere begins venting. Emergency repair kits are mounted on the wall nearby.

* [Grab the repair kit and patch the breach]
  ~ gain_radical("山")
  "山" (shān) — mountain, large rock
* [Help others evacuate first]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "救" (jiù) — to save, to rescue
* [Seal yourself in a safe compartment]
  ~ heal(10)
  "安" (ān) — safe, peaceful
* [Brave the decompression to salvage gear]
  ~ damage(10)
  "勇" (yǒng) — brave, courageous
